#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.156:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga "
msgstr "12. Hard Work "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.156:0.3"
msgid "156. Paṭhamameghasutta "
msgstr "156. Storms (1st) "

# NOTE: I don’t think akala can mean “out of season”. In fact, in the last month of summer, June/July, it rains quite frequently in the region.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.156:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gimhānaṃ pacchime māse ūhataṃ rajojallaṃ, tamenaṃ mahāakālamegho ṭhānaso antaradhāpeti vūpasameti; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, in the last month of summer, when the dust and dirt is stirred up, a large sudden storm disperses and settles it on the spot. "

msgctxt "sn45.156:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto uppannuppanne pāpake akusale dhamme ṭhānaso antaradhāpeti vūpasameti. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path disperses and stills bad, unskillful qualities on the spot. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.156:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto uppannuppanne pāpake akusale dhamme ṭhānaso antaradhāpeti vūpasameti? "
msgstr "How does a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path disperse and still bad, unskillful qualities on the spot? "

msgctxt "sn45.156:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn45.156:1.5"
msgid "evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto uppannuppanne pāpake akusale dhamme ṭhānaso antaradhāpeti vūpasametī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path disperses and stills bad, unskillful qualities on the spot.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.156:1.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

